04:58.709 --> 05:00.500
No, thank you.

04:58.709 --> 05:00.500
I am currently studying these

05:00.542 --> 05:02.875
informative motion pictures

05:00.542 --> 05:02.875
Cody provided me with.

05:03.875 --> 05:05.041
You're watching movies.

05:05.083 --> 05:06.959
I'm conducting

05:05.083 --> 05:06.959
research.

05:07.000 --> 05:09.166
Whatever you want

05:07.000 --> 05:09.166
