09:07.750 --> 09:09.917
He has been

09:07.750 --> 09:09.917
acting weird lately.

09:09.959 --> 09:11.625
I haven't noticed anything.

09:11.667 --> 09:14.166
His optics were clear,

09:11.667 --> 09:14.166
his spark pulse normal.

09:14.208 --> 09:16.000
There's an easy way

09:14.208 --> 09:16.000
to find out.

09:16.041 --> 09:18.291
Police Robot,

09:16.041 --> 09:18.291
report your 20.

09:19.750 --> 09:21.834
Chase is ignoring

09:19.750 --> 09:21.834
the Chief?

09:21.875 --> 09:24.834
Or more likely, he doesn't want

09:21.875 --> 09:24.834
to reveal his identity

09:24.875 --> 09:26.542
in front of those thieves.

09:28.208 --> 09:31.250
Dad, Chase just drove into a

09:28.208 --> 09:31.250
zone where the cameras are down.

09:31.291 --> 09:32.959
He must have

09:31.291 --> 09:32.959
some kind of plan.

09:33.000 --> 09:35.917
If he had a plan,

09:33.000 --> 09:35.917
he would've run it by me first.

09:35.959 --> 09:38.083
Maybe it's a secret plan.

09:38.125 --> 09:41.083
No, the Chase I know would

09:38.125 --> 09:41.083
never go rogue on a mission.

09:41.125 --> 09:43.667
Something's not right.

09:45.041 --> 09:47.000
MYLES:

09:45.041 --> 09:47.000
Stealing a police car?

09:47.041 --> 09:49.667
Chief Burns just got

09:47.041 --> 09:49.667
Chief Burn-ed.

09:49.709 --> 09:52.709
Let's take this baby outside

09:49.709 --> 09:52.709
and hook her up to big mama.

09:56.834 --> 09:58.917
Police log, undercover mission.

09:58.959 --> 10:01.709
Something tells me these

09:58.959 --> 10:01.709
two mugs are cooking up a plan

10:01.750 --> 10:03.959
so big they'll need

10:01.750 --> 10:03.959
an extra chili pot.

10:04.000 --> 10:08.625
I need to report their

10:04.000 --> 10:08.625
exact plan back to my chief.

10:08.667 --> 10:10.667
So I'm sticking around

10:08.667 --> 10:10.667
until I find out

10:10.709 --> 10:13.208
what they're serving

10:10.709 --> 10:13.208
for dessert.

10:13.250 --> 10:16.625
If X marks the spot,

10:13.250 --> 10:16.625
these goons are tic-tac-toeing

10:16.667 --> 10:18.125
their way to Doc's lab.

10:18.166 --> 10:21.125
Chief, Chase reporting in.

10:21.166 --> 10:22.834
Communications are blocked.

10:22.875 --> 10:26.083
My com is as useless

10:22.875 --> 10:26.083
as swim trunks in a sandbox.

10:26.125 --> 10:28.542
But maybe outside I--

10:26.125 --> 10:28.542
MYLES: Hey.

10:28.583 --> 10:31.709
Hold it right there, robot.

10:28.583 --> 10:31.709
Where do you think you're going?

10:31.750 --> 10:33.792
( robotic voice ):

10:31.750 --> 10:33.792
Awaiting input.

10:33.834 --> 10:35.917
Nice.

10:33.834 --> 10:35.917
Check it out bro.

10:35.959 --> 10:38.000
This hunk of junk

10:35.959 --> 10:38.000
has to do anything we say.

10:38.041 --> 10:40.834
Hey, CopBot.

10:38.041 --> 10:40.834
Change into a car.

10:43.750 --> 10:44.959
Now back to a robot.

10:48.083 --> 10:49.291
Hop on one foot.

10:51.125 --> 10:52.834
Do push-ups.

10:54.875 --> 10:56.834
Now act like

10:54.875 --> 10:56.834
