10:57.917 --> 10:59.667
( both laughing )

10:59.709 --> 11:01.750
Uh...

11:01.792 --> 11:05.000
Huh?

11:01.792 --> 11:05.000
Oh, you're evil, bro.

11:05.041 --> 11:08.208
Okay, robot,

11:05.041 --> 11:08.208
repeat after me,

11:08.250 --> 11:12.542
"Evan and Myles rule,

11:08.250 --> 11:12.542
the Burnses just drool."

11:12.583 --> 11:13.875
( sighs )

11:13.917 --> 11:15.583
( robotic voice ):

11:13.917 --> 11:15.583
Evan and Myles rule,

11:15.625 --> 11:17.667
the Burnses just drool.

11:17.709 --> 11:19.667
( both laugh )

11:19.709 --> 11:20.875
Yeah.

11:20.917 --> 11:22.834
New orders, gear brain.

11:22.875 --> 11:24.667
Steal us some floatium

11:22.875 --> 11:24.667
from the lab.

11:25.709 --> 11:27.208
I said move it.

11:30.709 --> 11:32.041
( engine starts )

11:37.917 --> 11:39.542
It's too perfect.

11:39.583 --> 11:42.625
Robo-dude takes the fall for us,

11:39.583 --> 11:42.625
