11:42.667 --> 11:44.875
to finish our rocking plan.

11:47.208 --> 11:48.834
Police log,

11:47.208 --> 11:48.834
undercover mission.

11:48.875 --> 11:50.834
I knew I was in deep.

11:50.875 --> 11:53.917
But Chief needed to know

11:50.875 --> 11:53.917
what these leeches had planned.

11:53.959 --> 11:55.875
So I had to go deeper.

11:55.917 --> 11:59.667
It was time

11:55.917 --> 11:59.667
to take off my swimmies.

11:59.709 --> 12:00.917
( powering up )

12:03.166 --> 12:05.250
( roaring )

12:05.291 --> 12:07.500
Down, Trex.

12:05.291 --> 12:07.500
Good boy.

12:07.542 --> 12:09.875
( cooing )

12:11.083 --> 12:13.083
( alarm beeping )

12:15.875 --> 12:19.583
Floatium, in its pure form,

12:15.875 --> 12:19.583
